settings.custom_liquid:
{% comment %}
  Template: Returns & Exchanges
  This page provides details on return policies, exchange procedures, and eligibility.
{% endcomment %}

<div class="returns-exchanges-container">
  <h1>Returns & Exchanges</h1>

  <section class="returns-section">
    <h2>Our Return Policy</h2>
    <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you're not happy, you can return your order within <strong>7 days</strong> of receiving it.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Items must be unworn, unused, and in their original packaging.</li>
      <li>Returns must be initiated within 7 days of delivery.</li>
      <li>Shipping fees are non-refundable.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="returns-section">
    <h2>How to Initiate a Return</h2>
    <p>To return an item, follow these steps:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a> with your order number and reason for return.</li>
      <li>We will review your request and provide return instructions.</li>
      <li>Once we receive your item, we will inspect it and process your refund within 5-7 business days.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="returns-section">
    <h2>Exchanges</h2>
    <p>If you need a different size or color, we offer exchanges within 7 days of delivery.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Exchanges are subject to availability.</li>
      <li>You must return the original item before the new one is shipped.</li>
      <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a> to request an exchange.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="returns-section">
    <h2>Non-Returnable Items</h2>
    <p>Certain items cannot be returned, including:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Personalized or custom-made products.</li>
      <li>Gift cards and promotional items.</li>
      <li>Items marked as final sale.</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="returns-section">
    <h2>Need Help?</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out at <a href="mailto:trezon.in@gmail.com">trezon.in@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </section>
</div>

<style>
  .returns-exchanges-container {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 20px;
    background: #EEDFA4; /* Background color */
    border-radius: 10px;
  }
  .returns-section {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .returns-section h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .returns-section p, .returns-section ul, .returns-section ol {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #333;
  }
  .returns-section ul, .returns-section ol {
    margin-left: 20px;
  }
  .returns-section a {
    color: #392D00;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .returns-section a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
